Package: MixviR
Title: Explore Genetic/Amino Acid Variation In Short Read Sequence Data From Mixed Microbial Samples - Esp Sars-Cov2
Version: 2.0.0.0000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Michael",
           family = "Sovic",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "sovic.1@osu.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8556-3704"))
Description: Provides functions to explore, characterize, and visualize genetic and amino acid variation from short-read DNA sequence samples that potentially contain mixtures of variants/lineages. Originally created to help analyze Sars-Cov2 (Covid19) data from wastewater and dust samples.
